  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>Istria</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>Pronounce<em> ['istry-ay]</em>.\n        Peninsula currently belonging to the republic of Croatia,\n        but formerly belonging to Austria-Hungary and Venice.\n        Herod relates in his <em>history</em> how Eatarchus\n        confused the Ister for the Nile and thus Itria for Egypt,\n        whence Antony's army departs for battle with Caesar. </font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>Istria and \"Burbank\"</td>\n<td><a href=\"Portrait175_JJ.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Istria_H.htm\">Istria\n                in Herod</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Istria and the Nile</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Sir Ferdinand Klein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Istria Pronounce ['istry-ay] . Peninsula currently belonging to the republic of Croatia, but formerly belonging to Austria-Hungary and Venice. Herod relates in his history how Eatarchus confused the Ister for the Nile and thus Itria for Egypt, whence Antony's army departs for battle with Caesar. reference topics Istria and \"Burbank\" Istria in Herod Istria and the Nile Sir Ferdinand Klein back to \"Burbank\"",
